{"tid":1001584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【改名注意】中國公布2018最熱門新生嬰兒名字","createTime":"2019-01-30T09:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T12:37:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b744f97d397c2b4e7463c4f42e7c78ccb2c93169","tid":1001584,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190130/s00004/2986c8add680988170ba263f93bc652e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190130%2Fs00004%2F2986c8add680988170ba263f93bc652e.jpg&h=afd9af93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190130/s00004/29954984b077a8d8f69f589f019e568c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190130%2Fs00004%2F29954984b077a8d8f69f589f019e568c.jpg&h=68403f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地公安部戶政管理研究中心透過覆蓋全國近14億人的人口信息系統，及使用大數據技術，統計並分析去年公安機關登記的全國姓氏和新生兒姓名用字情况，今日發表報告。全國最多人使用的姓氏，依次是「王」、「李」、「張」、「劉」及「陳」等；若男女嬰合計，最多新生兒使用的名字，依次是「梓涵」、「一諾」、「浩宇」、「欣怡」和「浩然」等。<br />\n<br />\n據統計，目前全國在用姓氏共有6150個。頭10個最多人用的姓氏依次是：「王」、「李」、「張」、「劉」、「陳」、「楊」、「黃」、「趙」、「吳」、「周」，其中姓「王」或「李」的人數都超過1億。<br />\n<br />\n新生兒名字中，使用率最高的首10個字為「梓」、「宇」、「子」、「涵」、「澤」、「雨」、「佳」、「浩」、「欣」、「軒」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，最多新生男嬰使用的頭10個名字分別是「浩宇」、「浩然」、「宇軒」、「宇航」、「宇澤」、「梓豪」、「子軒」、「浩軒」、「宇辰」、「子豪」。<br />\n<br />\n而最多新生女嬰使用的名字依次是「梓涵」、「一諾」、「欣怡」、「詩涵」、「依諾」、「欣妍」、「雨桐」、「梓萱」、「可馨」、「佳怡」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190130/s00004/1548835185194/2018全國各逾1億人姓「王」姓「李」-「梓涵」成最多新生嬰名字\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190130%2Fs00004%2F1548835185194%2F2018%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%84%E9%80%BE1%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%A7%93%E3%80%8C%E7%8E%8B%E3%80%8D%E5%A7%93%E3%80%8C%E6%9D%8E%E3%80%8D-%E3%80%8C%E6%A2%93%E6%B6%B5%E3%80%8D%E6%88%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F%E5%AC%B0%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfByWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9a30d1bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190130%2Fs00004%2F1548835185194%2F2018%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%84%E9%80%BE1%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%A7%93%E3%80%8C%E7%8E%8B%E3%80%8D%E5%A7%93%E3%80%8C%E6%9D%8E%E3%80%8D-%E3%80%8C%E6%A2%93%E6%B6%B5%E3%80%8D%E6%88%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F%E5%AC%B0%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97&h=66b44872\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190130/s00004/1548835185194/2018全國各逾1億人姓「王」姓「李」-「梓涵」成最多新生嬰名字</a>"},{"pid":"e4b2681aec7e87bf3c554e1d7d8a1be8b3807d4d","tid":1001584,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"冇 近 同 平？<br />\n<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddabf41c397e34f8e00f01588a6203d476d1e5a8","tid":1001584,"uid":39200,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e4b2681aec7e87bf3c554e1d7d8a1be8b3807d4d","tid":1001584,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"冇 近 同 平？<br />\n<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"同皇帝撞名驚過唔到滿月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4b436736559d216f92b0da0b397ce582bf2fd1","tid":1001584,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ddabf41c397e34f8e00f01588a6203d476d1e5a8","tid":1001584,"uid":39200,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e4b2681aec7e87bf3c554e1d7d8a1be8b3807d4d","tid":1001584,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"冇 近 同 平？<br />\n<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"同皇帝撞名驚過唔到滿月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"又係喎，on9咗添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hah